    <p>TV and ra­dio per­son­al­i­ties are cit­i­zens and con­tribut­ing mem­bers of so­ci­ety just like the rest of the com­mu­nity. They are gov­erned by the same laws and rules.</p>
    <p>And their choices come with re­spon­si­bil­i­ties and con­se­quences.</p>
    <p>Flout­ing the rules that safe­guard fel­low res­i­dents against Covid-19 is a se­ri­ous lapse of judg­ment (Me­di­a­corp artists may have flouted Covid-19 reg­u­la­tions, Dec 24).</p>
    <p>In fact, as celebri­ties, they ought to set an ex­am­ple to others.</p>


